:Description: trimmed input for use with Alquimia interface to Amanzi
:             for calcite dissolution

:=========================== chemistry ========================================
CHEMISTRY
  PRIMARY_SPECIES
    H+
    HCO3
    Ca++
  /
  SECONDARY_SPECIES
    OH-
    CO3--
    CO2(aq)
    CaOH+
    CaHCO3+
    CaCO3(aq)
  /
  MINERALS
    Calcite
  /
!  GAS_SPECIES
!    CO2(g)
!  /
  MINERAL_KINETICS
    Calcite
      RATE_CONSTANT 1.d-13 mol/cm^2-sec
    /
  /

  DATABASE ./calcite.dat
  LOG_FORMULATION
  ACTIVITY_COEFFICIENTS TIMESTEP
  OUTPUT
    All
    TOTAL
    FREE_ION
  /
  MAX_RESIDUAL_TOLERANCE 1.d-12
END

:=========================== constraints ======================================

CONSTRAINT LEFT
  CONCENTRATIONS
    H+     5.         P   
    HCO3  1.d-3      T   
    Ca++   1.d-2      Z   
  /
END

CONSTRAINT INITIAL
  CONCENTRATIONS
    H+     1.d-8      F   
    HCO3   1.d-3      T
    Ca++   5.d-4      M  Calcite
  /
  MINERALS
    Calcite 1.d-5 1.0d0 cm^2/cm^3
  /
END


